title: Raspberry Cream Cheese Tart Recipe Demonstration - Joyofbaking.com
description:
Recipe here: http://www.joyofbaking.com/RaspberryCreamCheeseTart.html Stephanie Jaworski of Joyofbaking.com demonstrates how to make a Raspberry Cream Cheese Tart. This Raspberry Cream Cheese Tart combines a wonderfully crisp and crumbly shortbread crust with a smooth and creamy custard-like filling that is dotted with juicy sweet fresh raspberries.

We welcome questions on our Facebook Page: http://www.facebook.com/joyofbaking
